        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In nomine domini Iesu Christi. Imperante donno nostro <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/9">Lothterius</persName> magno <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperatore</rs> agusto, in Dei nomine anni regnis
                        eius vigisimo quinto et donno nostro <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/110">Lodovvico</persName> filio eius glorioso rex
                        Langobardorum, hic in Italia anno tercio, die secundo mense magio, per
                        indicione sexta; acto ad <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1109">Sancti
                            Laurenci</orgName> in <placeName
                            key="#Churches #Cells/hermitages #Wood #Rivers #Land_clearing #Canals #Legumes #Wine #Maiores #Minores #Fruits/vegetables #Houses #Forests #Actionarii/actores #Rent_in_kind #Domuscultae #Operae #Exenia #Gai #Agricultural_workers #Petiae"
                            ref="#places/2492">Obstilia</placeName>
                        <rs key="#City_territory">terreturio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#City_territory" ref="#places/59">Veronensi</placeName>. A
                        vobis domno <persName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Abbots"
                            >Rapperti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasteri</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Cells/hermitages #Rent_in_kind #Domuscultae #Operae #Exenia #Gai #Agricultural_workers #Actionarii/actores #Petiae #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/47"><placeName key="#Monasteries"
                                ref="#places/15">Nonantole</placeName></orgName>, peto ego <persName
                            key="#Freeborn #Poultry #Eggs #Cows #Operae #Exenia"><name
                                ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Sergius">Sergi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Freeborn">livero homo</rs> uti nobis seo et filiis meis livellario
                        et massaricio nomine ad laborando et iustitja domnica persolvendo dare nobis
                        iubeatis de rem iure sagri monasteri vestri. Idest <rs key="#Petiae"
                            >pecia</rs> una de terra aratoria seo et <rs key="#Wood">frascario</rs>
                        exarata ad uno teniente super <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio Pado</rs> loco ubi
                        nominatur Obstilia finibus Veronensis, hoc est per mensura, ad pertica
                        legitima, lungo ipso fluvio Pado perticas viginti et sex et per lungo in <rs
                            key="#Forests">silva</rs> quanto <rs key="#Land_clearing">runcare</rs>
                        potueritis de terra bona, et est laterata ipsa pecia: da mane parte
                            <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Sabbatinus"
                                >Sabbatino</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">massario</rs> vestro abente, da meridio die
                        fluvio Pado percurrente, da sera <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name
                                ref="Paulus">Paulo</name></persName> item massario vestro abente, de
                        supto <rs key="#Gai">gagio</rs> domnico abente, et si quis aliis adfini sunt
                        ipsa peciam cum <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> et cum arboribus sui super se
                        abente. De quibus superio nominatis rebus promittimus adque spondimus
                        pariter et fideliter sine omnem nelictum vel fraude laborare et excollere et
                        super ipse res ressidere promittimus usque advenientibus annue numero
                        viginti et nove, casa seo et <rs key="#Canals">canalibus</rs> in ibidem
                        restaurare, curte, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">orto</rs>, aream faciendo et
                        claudere, vineam pastenare et propaginare, silva infructuosa roncare,
                        cithtera salvare, finem defensare et in omnibus meliorentur ne non
                        pegiorentur. <rs key="#Rent_in_kind">Et redere promittimus</rs> de
                        suprascripte rebus ad parte monasteri vestri de suprascripte rebus annue
                        tenporibus de omne genere grano quit super ipsa terra seminatum fuerit: de
                            <rs key="#Maiores">grano grosso</rs> in canpo cappa quarta, <rs
                            key="#Legumes">legumen</rs> vel <rs key="#Minores">menudo</rs> modio
                        quarto, lino manna quarta, <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs> anfora quarta
                        tritorato; omnium suprascripto redito in aream nostram et vegere et
                        cunsignare ad <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cella</rs> vestra in <placeName
                            key="#Cells/hermitages #Poultry #Eggs #Cows #Operae #Exenia #Actionarii/actores"
                            ref="#places/1538"><geogName
                                key="#Cells/hermitages #Poultry #Eggs #Cows #Operae #Exenia #Actionarii/actores"
                                ref="#estates/1111">Piscaria</geogName></placeName> cum nostro
                        dispengio. <rs key="#Exenia">Exenio</rs> per annue dare promitto, in
                        nativitatem Domini <rs key="#Poultry">pullo</rs> bono uno, <rs key="#Eggs"
                            >ovas</rs> quinque, et in pasca similiter, de orto unde non redatur, per
                        annue dare promitto in missa sancti Petri denariis sex. <rs key="#Operae"
                            >Opere</rs> per annue facere promittimus ad <rs key="#Domuscultae">casa
                            vestra</rs> in Obstilia per anno opere sex, medietatem cum <rs
                            key="#Cows">bovis</rs>, medietatem manualiter, cum annona domnica; et
                        per tenpus lavoris vel vino recolligendo, misso domnico cum onore
                        susscipiento et susscepta eis facere promittimus et braciatica eis dare. Et
                        sit de hec ista omnia minime fecierimus per <rs key="#Actionarii/actores"
                            >misso monasteri</rs> nostri districti et pignoratis esse debeamus. Pena
                        vero quidem inter nos anbas partis ponimus ut si quis pars partis contra hos
                        livelli ire tentavierimus, exire vel fraude nelicto fecierimus aut nos pars
                        dominacionis minare aut expellere aut aliqua superinposita fecierimus, tunc
                        promittimus conponere pars partis fidem servantis pena nomine in argenti
                        solidos duodicem et pos conposita pena hos livello in suam manea firmitatem.
                        + Scripta cartola per manum <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Victor">Victuri</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs>
                        <rs key="#Writer">conplivi</rs> et dedi.   </ab>
